text:
Selena Gomez Looks So In Love With Boyfriend Benny Blanco On Art Exhibit Date Night
Selena Gomez and Benny Blanco can’t keep their hands to themselves! The couple packed on the PDA for their date night at an art exhibit and the songstress posted photos of the romantic outing on her Instagram story. In one of the pics, Selena and Benny’s reflections can be seen in a pink mirrored ceiling and the 35-year-old music producer has his arms wrapped around the 31-year-old while she smiles! In another photo, Selena showed off her man with a solo shot that she took herself. The couple’s cute date night comes one week after the “Only Murders In The Building” star opened up in an interview with Vogue México y Latinoamérica, translated from Spanish, about what she’s looking for in a relationship. “Honestly, I have to start being attracted to the right kind of people, because it’s a bit of both. It’s very hard to find someone who can listen to you and care about you, but I know when it happens it will be great, and I will want it to be healthy,” she told the magazine.
